rows.label: tev066701_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Ni Zain about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066701_NSG0001
rows.name:
Once I have gained mastery of curry, I intend to test
my ladle against some regional variations as well.
Rare ingredients bring out the best in a chef![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066701_NSG0002
rows.name:
I was hoping to next attempt a red curry from that
most arcane of Nopon additivesâ€”a red pollen orb![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066701_NSG0003
rows.name:
But when Tatsu came by to sample my work and I
spoke of this endeavor, he dismissed it most frantically.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066701_NSG0004
rows.name:
A shame. I was so certain my red curry was just the
kick in the proverbial pants the world needed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066701_NSG0008
rows.name:
Ah! Behold, good [ST:playername ]!
I can hardly keep up with demand![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066701_NSG0010
rows.name:
In all my years of swinging a blade, I have never
conquered the hearts of others like this.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066701_NSG0011
rows.name:
I am simply overcome with gratitude to you and Meg
for teaching me the chefly arts.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066701_NSG0012
rows.name:
If only Prince Jiarg were here instead of in Oblivia.
Then he might taste what I have achieved![ST:wait ]
